### Crear servicio habilitado
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/enabled-services HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sedeId": 1,
    "serviceCode": "SRV-001",
    "serviceName": "Consulta Externa General",
    "modality": "PRESENCIAL",
    "complexity": "BAJA",
    "enablementDate": "2024-01-01",
    "expirationDate": "2026-12-31",
    "resolution": "RES-2024-001",
    "observations": "Servicio habilitado para atención primaria"
}

###

### Crear servicio habilitado sin vencimiento
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/enabled-services HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sedeId": 1,
    "serviceCode": "SRV-002",
    "serviceName": "Urgencias 24 horas",
    "modality": "PRESENCIAL",
    "complexity": "ALTA",
    "enablementDate": "2024-01-01",
    "resolution": "RES-2024-002"
}

###

### Obtener servicio habilitado por ID
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/enabled-services/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar servicios habilitados (sin búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/enabled-services/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "sh.nombre_servicio",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Listar servicios habilitados (con búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/enabled-services/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "consulta",
    "order_by": "sh.nombre_servicio",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Actualizar servicio habilitado
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/api/enabled-services/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "serviceName": "Consulta Externa General - Actualizada",
    "modality": "PRESENCIAL",
    "complexity": "MEDIA",
    "enablementDate": "2024-01-01",
    "expirationDate": "2027-12-31",
    "resolution": "RES-2024-001-A",
    "observations": "Actualización de complejidad"
}

###

### Activar / Inactivar servicio habilitado (toggle)
PATCH http://localhost:{{port}}/api/enabled-services/1/toggle-active HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
